 in a single fully integrated solution.</p></div></div></div><div class="container-fluid text-center well"> <h1>Control for Manufacturing<br><small>Integrate IT, Customer Service, and Projects into one with TeamHeadquarters</small></h1> </div><div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8"> <p class="lead">Help Desk and Project Management for Manufacturing. Fully integrated technology support, product development and project management.</p><h2>Manufacturing Technology Support</h2> <p>No longer is IT a distinct component of your business - it is your business. IT now supports your whole manufacturing environment. TeamHeadquarters makes it easy by integrating Help Desk and Project Management into a single application.</p><ul> <li>Employee support requests management</li><li>Defect tracking</li><li>Customer inquiries and help desk</li></ul> <h2>Product Development for Manufacturers</h2> <p>Complex and critical functions like Product Development are supported through TeamHeadquarters Project Management, issues and risks tracking and through custom portals.</p><ul> <li>Support for products</li><li>Planning</li><li>Project Management</li></ul> <h2>Project Management</h2> <p>Resource management and project scheduling are critical to a positive outcome. TeamHeadquarters removes the blindspots and keeps the road clear!</p><ul> <li>Internal and external customer project execution</li><li>Project planning and scheduling</li><li>Task assignment and management</li><li>Track bugs, risks and issues</li><li>Time tracking</li><li>Resource management</li></ul> </div><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4" style="background-color: darkorange; margin-bottom: 15px; padding-bottom: 15px;"> <h1>Manufacturers across the globe are adopting TeamHeadquarters!</h1> <p class="lead">Manufacturers are turning to TeamHeadquarters for straightforward and comprehensive tools to manage business. A demonstration for your team will help you see why.</p><a href="http://signup.entry.com/demonstration-manufacturing" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Register for Demonstration</a> <div class="thumbnail" style="margin-top: 15px;"> <img src="/img/otc-case-study-cta.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters manufacturing management helps business grow"> <div class="caption"> <h3>Case Study: Using TeamHQ to grow business</h3> <p>This case study examines the success of OTC in growing their business using TeamHeadquarters</p><p><a target="_blank" href="http://cdn2.hubspot.net/hubfs/210980/docs/OTC_case_study.pdf" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">Download Case Study</a></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="footer"> <?php include '../public_html/includes/footer.html';?> <?php include '../public_html/includes/google.html';?> </div></body></html>